#. (itstool) path: ul/li
#: org.kde.haruna.metainfo.xml:99
msgid ""
"Subtitles: if a relative folder name in the <_:code-1/> list starts with an "
"* (asterisk) then subtitles will be searched in all folders containing the "
"folder name. Example: If the <_:code-2/> list contains an entry <_:code-3/> "
"and you have the following folders next to the video file <_:code-4/>, <_:"
"code-5/> and <_:code-6/> all of these folders will be searched."
